Class FlickrSearch

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
Bindable, Introspectable, SourcesPropertyChangeEvents
public class FlickrSearch
extends AbstractModelBean

A bean that performs JSON-P calls the Flickr Feeds API. Any changes to the parameters (tags, user), will update the search result fields (title, phots).

rcooper
